    "description": "**CIS-1200 (T-230-1A Маховик)**, or \"**Flywheel**\" in Russian, is a PSK based mode that can transmit both voice and data. It is transmitted from a Russian T-230-1A. Has been seen with both BPSK and SDPSK manipulation at 1200Bd."
